title: Children Of Bodom - I Worship Chaos (Single) (2015)ak
description:
I Worship Chaos is the upcoming ninth studio album by Finnish melodic death metal band Children of Bodom. It will be released on October 2, 2015.[1] It is the first album without guitarist Roope Latvala since he left the band in May 2015, making this the band's first album as a four-piece group with Alexi Laiho handling all guitar duties.

For the first time, the band didn't use a commercial recording studio. Instead they opted to use a converted warehouse to enhance the ambiance of the sound.
